{
  "stem": "766.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, five o'clock, they hardly had a few hours' sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all were wearing the-- the Holland shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- The clogs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The clogs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they came back, they marched miles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all have cut the-- the-- the-- the-- the-- the-- the skin here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I bandaged with this paper band-aid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before I finished, it was already ripped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so the-- the-- the-- the wound was deeper and deeper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it never healed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over they were mostly young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they needed-- they didn't do hard, physical work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they selected them to do-- it was with wires.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few, 14.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "15.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why do I remember this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Hungarian, they were the youngest and kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they-- I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They all speak-- from Budapest, they all speak German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the supervisor, the German who asked me what's my-- my crime, once came to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had pity on them, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, you know, take these three girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were kids, 15 years, maybe 12, and make them sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And let them work in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not in the hospital, but in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So meanwhile, they will eat potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you-- you don't-- they didn't count the potatoes over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and let them recover a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in the first moment, I thought maybe she wants to trick me in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, so even if, let it be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she didn't really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were [? a bit-- ?] but it didn't help them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one said my father was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came to see, somewhere-- I came to see my grandmother and they caught me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
